title: Biomass Processing Technologies - Vladimir Strezov and Tim J. Ev
description:
Biomass Processing Technologies - Vladimir Strezov and Tim J. Evans (CRC, 2015).pdf

ISBN 978-1-4665-6616-3

This text is a thoroughly up-to-date treatment of all the available technologies for biomass conversion. Each chapter looks at the viability and implementation of each technology with examples of existing equipment and plants. In addition, the text addresses the economics of biomass processing. The book could also be used as a supplementary text for senior undergraduate courses on biomass processing
